## 18 · Review rows added to main plan §5

These rows, added to the main plan's review checklist, make tests first-class in every PR review:

| Row | Check |
|---|---|
| R19 | Every issue in `Fixes:` has a matching `TestRegression_Issue<N>_*` present in the diff or already in the tree |
| R20 | Any new safety-critical function is bound to a named subtest under the appropriate rule file |
| R21 | Any new goroutine is covered by a test that exercises its lifecycle including cancellation |
| R22 | Any new backend implementation passes `TestHAL_Contract` for its channel kind |
| R23 | Any new public metric, route, or config field is reflected in the corresponding docs golden test |

